Description: Provides an integrated and user-friendly workflow for
    analyzing transcriptomic data, including RNA-Seq and microarray
    experiments.  Implements automated data preprocessing with
    normalization and batch effect correction, multi-model classification
    with feature selection, consensus biomarker identification, and robust
    external validation. Offers extensive visualizations—such as PCA,
    PVCA, AUROC, UpSet plots, and heatmaps—to facilitate data exploration
    and model evaluation. Enables reproducible biomarker discovery by
    combining multiple machine learning classifiers and consensus
    approaches, helping researchers identify and validate robust gene
    signatures.
